Even more interesting…

I think PALM has an implicit inverse.

If PALM performs

morphology → history

then another operator naturally exists:

history → morphology

That’s your Compiler.

Compiler predicts the structure that should emerge.

PALM reconstructs the process that produced the structure.

One is forward simulation.

One is inverse inference.

Together they form another dual pair in the Pantheon algebra.

